INSERT INTO `review` VALUES (1,1,0,2,'<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">TotalAV is a new player in the antivirus industry that has significantly gained immense popularity, following its incomparable traits and bundled capabilities to provide real-time protection against malicious programs and online threats at affordable prices (lower promotional prices to new customers for the initial term). One distinctive feature that sets apart TotalAV from other competitors, is the ability to utilize a very minimal processing power of the base systems while running.<span style=\"color: rgb(74, 74, 74); background-color: white;\"> </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">TotalAV is an incredible antivirus product that implements the “same antivirus Tech” like <strong>Avira</strong>, making it strike the balance between using a highly-respected VPN provider Windscribe and the best Canadian-produced VPN technology. This product (TotalAV) comes in both commercial (<em>Pro, Internet Security, Total Security)</em> and free-trial versions operating on a 30-day money-back guarantee. Also, they are supported by numerous platforms including Windows, Android, Mac OS, Linux, and iOS.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">All these features plus different scanning options,&nbsp;real-time protection, and a firewall capability in the TotalAV Antivirus Pro package make them worth trying. <strong>Note: </strong>the free version has a demonstrated efficacy in protecting (scanning and detecting) against threats no matter what.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Just like any security utility, TotalAV also comes with a handful of Pros and Cons, Let’s, therefore, uncover some of those <strong>pros and cons&nbsp;</strong></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Note:</strong> With the existence of so many antivirus suites globally, it\'s quite daunting for the users, especially beginners to make a solid and unremorseful decision in the antivirus arena. Besides, there is a sharp shift towards the control and safety protection of online and personal data. To address these challenges, we pointed out some potential questions that the said users can brainstorm on.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How effective are the security elements of the antivirus product?</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Is it easy to use the antivirus product? If so, what about the customer’s support services?</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What are the platform supports for the product</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Does the product offer money for values in terms of their pricing plans? etc</p>','[{\"value\":\"An excellent suite of common features\"},{\"value\":\"More transparent auto-renewal policies\"},{\"value\":\"Intuitive and downright attractive UI with VPN feature\"},{\"value\":\"24/7 customer service\"},{\"value\":\"Strong protection against malicious URL\"}]','[{\"value\":\"Slow quick scan time\"},{\"value\":\"No real-time protection with the free version\"},{\"value\":\"Requires account creation to install, even with a free version\"},{\"value\":\"No real-time protection with the free version\"}]','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Security and reliability:</strong></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">When it comes to the security field, TotalAV provides a huge range of features starting from the <strong><em>standard protection</em></strong> against the various scope of malware, to <strong><em>real-time antivirus protection</em></strong> and <strong><em>firewall protection</em></strong>, not forgetting <strong><em>web shield and safe browsing</em></strong> respectively.</p><p>The product (TotalAV) provides two major types of scans namely, Quick and System Scan. The beauty here is, users can run their scan and continue doing other work without affecting the performance of their systems. Upon completion of the scan, users are availed with options to&nbsp;<em>quarantine, delete, whitelist, or ignore each malware file</em>. Which allows them to respond appropriately.</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"502\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">TotalAV also presents another exquisite security feature called <strong>password vault</strong> (Password Vault browser extension), that enables users to securely store, organize, and retrieve all their login credentials. Lastly, the TotalAV’s<strong> System Tune-Up </strong>feature is very handy to maintain the smooth running of the user’s computer<strong> </strong>on top of freeing up disk space and deleting unnecessary information Vulnerable to privacy.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Via <strong><em>reliability</em></strong><em>,</em> TotalAV is a new kid on the block that has not undergone rigorous lab tests (third-party independent tests). It is therefore cumbersome to confirm its efficiency at the moment.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">As far as the compatility of devices and platforms are concern, TotalAV run across most of the Operating Systems and Devices in used nowdays as indicated below.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"518\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Additionally they can also be used on the Linux distributions. That said, the application work on desktops, laptops, cellphones, tablets, etc.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Via browser’s compatiblity, TotalAV extends their supports to several types of browsers like Google chrome, Mozilla firefox, Safari, and Microsoft edge as indicated below.</p><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"501\"></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">One of the commendable features that put TotalAV on top of their game is the user-friendliness. The TotalAV is lauded for coming up with a product very easy to use and a good user interface that constitutes a neat dashboard displaying most of the essential features as indicated in the image below.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"549\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><em>Still, on ease of use</em>, the down and installation process of this product is lighting fast and intuitive when compared to other competitors like Bitdefender. <strong>However</strong>, It is a <strong>must</strong> for the user\'s to first create their account before starting to use the products. Hence a constraint cutting across free and paid packages.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">TotalAV is highly rated for its far-reaching customer supports. It is one of the Products that implement 24/7 technical support and customer services regardless of the package’s subscription. Mechanism deployed includes the Knowledge Base fully loaded a bunch of answers and support to the FAQs, guides on download, installation, and uninstallation of the packages, etc.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Customers can quickly access the Tutorials and videos with handy articles that tackle essentials topics example how to reset a password and many others. Technical or Non-Technical support can further be delivered through email, telephone, and live chat on their official website.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">For users planning to opt for a paid version of TotalAV, there are three main commercial packages to choose from, these are <em>(i) antivirus Pro</em> (up to 3 devices), <em>(ii)</em> <em>Internet Security</em> (up to 5 devices<em>), </em>and <em>(iii)Total Security</em> (up to 6 devices) as indicated in the images below.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"578\" style=\"cursor: nesw-resize;\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">At the time of writing this review, new users can get any of the three packages at very stunning promotional prices. For the initial buy, the prices of the Total AV suites are as indicated below.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">According to the TotalAV’s official site, All services automatically renew at the regular rate using the same payment method (PayPal or Credit card), unless you request a change. Prices exclude VAT.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Note: </strong>for any user in need of a solitary license, the most basic plan “Essential Antivirus,” comes with one license at an initial rate of $19.95. This can be a big deal for them.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Also, doubtful users who might need to first try the product before full engagement can freely download and use the trial version of TotalAV (with limited antivirus functionalities like scanning malware).</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Lastly, TotalAV offers a 30-day money-back guarantee that allows any user to request back their fund in a scenario where they are not happy with the services provided</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">For a rookie company like TotalAV, there has been a tremendous improvement in their performance, user experience, and interface. These are pure manifestations that, the product has got a bright future ahead.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">However, one undeniable truth is, this product still <strong>lacks cutting-edge security functionalities</strong>, a constraint that might prevent it from being a leader in antivirus business, if not fixed.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">All in all, it is still one of the antivirus products very worth checking out.</p>','2020-06-12 02:10:55','2020-06-19 08:47:19',NULL),(4,4,0,2,'<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">iolo is a wholly-owned subsidiary of&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.phoenix.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: black;\">Phoenix Technologies Ltd</a>, Founded in 1998 and headquartered in Los Angeles, California. The ultimate reason behind the foundation of this company was to investigate the causes, and develop solutions for the problems of system’s slowdowns, crashes and system freezes. After numerous years of research, iolo Labs nowadays develops patented technology and award-winning software that repairs, optimize, and protects computers and digital devices, enabling users to enjoy their full computing potential by keeping devices running fast and reliably. This has made <strong>iolo</strong> globally recognized as both the consumer and industry expert in system utility software market in 2001, for incorporating <strong>System Mechanic tool</strong> into its (iolo\'s) commercially tune-up products available.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">This tool comes in three different flagships namely: System Mechanic, System Mechanic Pro,<strong> </strong>and System Mechanic Ultimate Defense. Out of all these, <strong>System Mechanic Ultimate Defense&nbsp;</strong>is a comprehensive package for all your security, privacy, and performance needs all in a convenient interface. It is built on the PC performance foundation of System Mechanic, thereby adding the <strong>real-time Antivirus</strong> and data protection features of System Mechanic Pro ontop of secured user’s web browsing, passwords &amp; credit cards management, and on-demand malware removal.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">That said, it is worth knowing that, iolo currently operates in 33 countries and the products are presented in 11 languages, whereby tens of millions of clients have subscribed to the products for their PC optimization, security, and data recovery.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">As aforementioned, <a href=\"https://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=kXQk6*ivFEQ&amp;offerid=372856.10000264&amp;type=3&amp;subid=0\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: black;\">iolo System Mechanic Ultimate Defense</a>&nbsp;is the new name for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.techradar.com/in/reviews/iolo-phoenix-360\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: black;\">iolo Phoenix 360</a>, a company renown for its fully-fledge bundle for the PC cleanup and security packages. It also presents to the market new tech to avert modern online threats and a new design that brings it in line with Iolo’s other software.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">With this excerpt overview, we can now swing to the action and dissect some of the intriguing reviews of this PC utility. But, first, let\'s list out some of the potential queries every savvy computer users might ask him or herself while looking for any utility to protect their privacy and bolster their security.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How effective is the utility in providing robust security for their users</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Does it have reliable customer support services</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What about the pricing policies? Is it worth, money for value?</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What platforms and devices are compatible with the tool in question ?</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">In summary, below is a break down of the features of iolo security utilities, from System Mechanic, System Mechanic Pro, to System Mechanic Ultimate Defense.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"547\"></p>','[{\"value\":\"Effective cleanup and security tools\"},{\"value\":\"Well designed and easy to use interface\"},{\"value\":\"Excellent value\"}]','[{\"value\":\"Not all tools have one-click fixes\"}]','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">System Mechanic generally deploy a module that deals with Windows security issues, personal data sharing, and permanently deleting malicious files.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Some of these privacy and security tools include Privacy Guardian, Password manager Bye-Pass, and Malware Killer (an app for malicious software cleanup).</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">To begin with, <strong>Privacy Guardian</strong> is a feature designed, for protecting user’s personal information while connected online. The tool works by implementing “<strong>anti-fingerprinting techniques</strong>” that literally block the tracker that typically follows the user’s browsing activities from site to site. <strong>Note</strong>: When these trackers are not blocked, they can be used to create a profile to target users with personalized ads and other content. This is where anti-fingerprinting<strong> </strong>becomes very useful and<strong> </strong>it further avails the users with a precise record of how many times they have been protected from being profiled, on top of knowing sites tracking them.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Additionally, the <strong>Bye-Pass</strong> feature is a secure password generator and manager that operates by storing all user\'s logins in a single encrypted vault secured with a master password. This feature distinguished itself from other password managers by supporting two-factor authentication, which enables users to secure payment details and notes<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: white;\">.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Furthermore, the <strong>Malware Killer</strong> and <strong>System Shield</strong> are yet another security features. In practice, Malware Killer helps to defends users PC from malicious software – not only by blocking known threats but also by removing existing infections. To accomplish these, it (Malware Killer) uses an extensive cloud-based database and heuristic analysis techniques to detect threats and pick up suspicious programs. While System Shield on the iolo antivirus apps is simple to use, it also has the capability of scheduling scans. Below is an interface of the system shield feature.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"510\"></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">One of the key characteristics that set apart iolo System Mechanic from the rest of other PC tune-up utilities is the capability to allow subscribers (users) to install the software on any number of computers, so long as&nbsp;it\'s not for business purposes. This is, therefore, a tremendous benefit of the whole Home License (multi-PC environment)</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">This tool is compatible with several browsers for its Privacy Guardian feature, including, Firefox, Chrome, Windows Explorer, Opera, and Edge. For the ByePass functionalities, it only works with Chrome and Firefox although Support for other browsers is under progress.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Via Operating system’s support, Iolo System Mechanic is in partnership with Microsoft. This makes it compatible with all PCs running Windows XP and later (up to Windows 10).</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">In terms of user experience, the utility comes shoved without any irritating software, browser extensions or other clutter, This makes the installation and general use of the application very easy and convenient.</p>','<p>When it comes to the user’s support, iolo’s System Mechanic posit itself as a fair player. Like any other antivirus utilities, System Mechanic also uses its knowledge base, fully fed with a pool of articles and solutions regarding user’s queries. Next, it has a community forum where announcements, sales, and offers are concisely displayed for both new and regular users. However, these supports services are categorized in Free Product Support and Premium Support.</p><p><strong>Note:</strong> The unlimited 24/7 support services are only supported by the premium package.</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"564\"></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">iolo System Mechanic costs around $49.95 per year, meanwhile, System Mechnic Pro package can go for about $69.95-per-year. This is literally expensive, but a perfect match for the “value for money” since the suite contains&nbsp;<a href=\"https://in.pcmag.com/antivirus-from-pc-ma/34241/the-best-antivirus-protection\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: black;\">antivirus</a>, anti-spyware, and anti-malware tools with the standard tune-up package. One thing to note though, these products run perpetually with discounts, so users should not get worried about paying the full amount.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">To track the variation in the prices and discounts, users should feel free to pay a visit to the Iolo security site. On top of the discount, customers can also enjoy a <strong>30 day trial period</strong> for the products.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">iolo’s System Mechanic Ultimate Defense is a fully-fledged security suite for protecting users from online threats. This software also includes antivirus, a secure password manager, a drive wiper, anti-tracking tools for your web browser, malware detection and removal, and a file recovery tool in addition to PC cleanup tools. The suite demonstrates a total refurbishment with impressive results in PC performance and security of each component being effective and simple to use.</p>','2020-06-16 02:48:49','2020-06-19 08:48:01',NULL),(5,3,0,2,'<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">BullGuard is an award-winning Cybersecurity company formed by <strong>Danish</strong> entrepreneurs with over <strong>18 years</strong> of operation, and still in counting, known for their “<em>industry innovating leadership</em>”. Their conviction is consolidated in making simple security products to protect users or organizational data, integrity, and privacy to bolster their (subscriber’s) confidence to use the internet in absolute safety.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">This company (BullGuard) offers a comprehensive range of security and privacy solutions which are packaged as <em>(i) BullGuard Antivirus (ii) BullGuard Internet Security and (iii) BullGuard Premium Protection</em>. The BullGuard Antivirus, in particular, provides a great (triple-layered) protection against all types of malware such as Trojans or phishing attempts designed to steal users (banking) information. It operates with three guiding pillars to <em>“identify, isolates and neutralizes”</em> all types of viruses and malware families.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Recently, the company has joined the wagon to implement <strong>Advance Machine Learning</strong> and <strong>Secure Browsing</strong> in their arsenal of tools, with refined mathematical algorithms and deep learning methods to deliver superfast threat detection against emerging and advanced threats thus, thwarting zero-day threats and other associated advanced types of malware. Also, the new version of BullGuard antivirus 2020 edition,(at the time of writing this review), provides stunning features like <strong>Next-Gen Antimalware </strong>(recognizes trusted sites and applications through intelligent triple layer protection), <strong>Game Booster </strong>(enables gaming in absolute safety without compromising security for performance), and <strong>Vulnerability Scanner </strong>(uses a digital signature to check the authenticity of application and drivers). The portfolio of BullGuard’s product covers numerous devices like PC, Mac, Tablets, Smartphones, etc.&nbsp;</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Every antivirus product out there is presented with Pros and Cons, and this award-winning product (BullGuard antivirus) is <strong>not</strong> exceptional. Let’s now take a quick look at some of the merits and demerits associated with BullGuard.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">With the above assessment (Pros and Cons), any antivirus users can get a glimpse of what solution is incorporated with the Bullguard products. Before we slice down the reviews, here are some of the questions that everyone must ponder about.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What are the package features of BullGuard?</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;What essential security features does it implement? And how is it reliable</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How about in terms of pricing, how does it fare in the market</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Does it support most Platforms?</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">·&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;How effective is their customer’s support services?</p>','[{\"value\":\"Antivirus protection is above average\"},{\"value\":\"excellent design and usability\"},{\"value\":\"Compatible with most OS including earlier versions of Windows like Vista (32 and 64)\"},{\"value\":\"Good scores from 3rd-party labs\"},{\"value\":\"High Detection rates with phishing protection  above average\"}]','[{\"value\":\"Long installation\"},{\"value\":\"Parental control isn’t nearly as advanced compared to those of their competitors\"}]','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">To begin with the security aspect, Bullguard is one of the solutions that has undergone vigorous tests by many third-party labs. One test conducted by a highly cherished antiviruses testing company (AV-Comparatives), Posits BullGuard as a champion in virus detection with real-time scanning.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Some security features include Quick, full, and custom scanning options&nbsp;along with a&nbsp;quarantine zone to allow users to delete or release suspicious files, vulnerability scanner to scan potentially harmful practices, Firewall protection, malware protection, URL blocking, Parental Control, and many others.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The recent AV-Comparative test reflected that BullGuard is 100% able to block known malware, while the capability to block zero-day attack stands at 99%. Also, Anti-phishing protection is quite remarkable. Better still, the URL blocking performance is above the average<span style=\"color: rgb(42, 42, 42); background-color: white;\"> </span>standard with a score of 89%. All these ultimately place it (BullGuard) among the top 10 antivirus solutions in the market.</p>','','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">When it comes to usability, BullGuard is very impressive and rated among the top 3 products in the arena. The ease of use is exhibited in various ways, firstly the download and installation process has explicit and user-friendly procedures. Also, the User interface is very intuitive and well-designed with most of the features are at first glance to the scribers, on top of these, there is a simple notification counter that sits above the dashboard very helpful for the users to view any issues requiring attention.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"505\"></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">BullGuard delivers its support and services to the client in a very professional manner using live chat, e-mail, and an on-site ticket system (login trouble ticket). The email support is operated in 12 different languages including English, Spanish, and Chinese among others.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Their live chat runs on a 24/7 basis with a quick response from the designated agents on duty who always have the technical expertise to explain the product’s dynamics to the clients.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"455\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Users can also visit BullGuard’s official site or social media platforms (Facebook or Twitter) for a quick response to their questions. Alternatively, there is a section for FAQs that are flirty rich with manuals to guide users.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Similarly, their community forums and blogs are always active and regularly updated.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Note: </strong>BullGuard<strong> </strong>does not provide phone supports.&nbsp;</p>','<p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"455\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">As depicted above, BullGuard comes in three major flavors, thus giving vast options for the users to make stress free decisions in their picks. <strong>Note</strong>, the premium protection is far expensive if you are protecting only one PC. But when you are operating in a multi-device environment, this can be the best option considering the number of simultaneous device support and the prices.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">There is also one extra Product (BullGuard Mobile Security) that can go for around – $19.95/year. For user’s not willing to subscribe to these commercial packages, there is a 15 days trial (BullGuard antivirus) and 30 days for BullGuard Internet security and premium protection respectively.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">All these paid editions offer a 30-day money-back guarantee&nbsp;</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Antivirus users looking for a solution with easy usability, high detection rates, and some useful add-ons plus Vulnerability Scanner, Game Booster, PC TuneUp, Identity Protection, and Password Manager all at an affordable price. BullGuard is products you shouldn\'t miss trying.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The bottom line is, regardless of the package you subscribe to, all of them (packages) use the same antivirus engine. Although, if you want some extra features, you can decide for yourself.</p>','2020-06-16 02:57:54','2020-06-19 08:47:53',NULL);
INSERT INTO `review` VALUES (6,5,0,1,'<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Panda is one of the pioneers on the antivirus eco-systems coined by a Spanish multinational company dubbed, “panda security”. This antivirus (recently rebranded Panda Dome) has been in the industry of protecting computer users and systems for 30 years and, still in counting. Its design is primarily geared towards detecting malware on user’s devices before any damage or havoc happens. That said, Panda antivirus presents an award-wining smart technology system that allows constant monitoring of virtually everything transpiring in users\' systems. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">The antivirus (Panda) tool, comes in both free and commercial versions. The panda free-antivirus version has no strings with much focus on core antivirus engine, while the Panda commercial’s package covers everything from a basic antivirus product for most operating systems (like Windows, Mac, and Android) to a full security suite with parental controls, banking and shopping protection, extra anti-ransomware capabilities, encryption, and a password manager plus unlimited VPN use.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Panda antivirus has relentlessly upheld its super </span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">reputation</span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> to offer several incredible features that are resourceful: to keep</span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\"> user’s PC and devices safe, protect their privacy, and optimize the devices’ performance</span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">. Other impeccable features include personalized firewall configuration, cryptojacking protection, and customizable ransomware protection just to mention but a few.</span></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">For individual users or organizations connecting always to the web (internet), with their computers, they need to check the following pros and cons to make a solid decision while opting for this brand of antivirus solution.&nbsp;</span></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Reading through the </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Pros and Cons </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">is of paramount importance but, it is by far better to peruse through the comprehensive review sections to have an expounded idea about Panda’s security product. Below are the reviews.</span></p>','[{\"value\":\"Affordable prices and a wide choice of plans\"},{\"value\":\"Provide extra security safety like the option for firewall configuration for advanced users\"},{\"value\":\"Machine learning and AI helps in threat hunting\"},{\"value\":\"Free VPN included in many plans\"},{\"value\":\"Simple and appealing interface\"}]','[{\"value\":\"Lack of ransomware protection with the cheapest plan\"},{\"value\":\"24/7 technical support available only with Panda’s premium plan\"}]','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Security is regarded as the process of securing information from unauthorized access. The process incorporates preventing unauthorized access, disclosure, inspection, modification and destruction of an organization’s or individual information. This is where Panda antivirus chips-in and plays a crucial role.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Panda product is rated for having checked almost all essential security features required for optimal protection against threats. Based on numerous lab tests, this antivirus tools can detect every single malware attacks including those previously unknown to the system users. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">With the recent update to its new Dome suites, Panda antivirus product offers </span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">enhanced protection and provision of cutting edge tools to protect users </span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">from the many web-associated threats (like a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">virus, Trojan horse, worms, botnets, etc). </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">Some of the revamped, Panda’s security feature include (i) suite of tools that defend user’s privacy, including the company’s Wi-Fi protection and VPN, (ii) virtual keyboard which can be used when logging in to websites and entering user’s password, (iii) the antivirus scanner that offers systematic protection and quick display of results after finding potential threat. This scanner helps to check problems ranging from the malware to ransomware and, any USB device plugged into the computers. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Note:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> Panda antivirus, like any other scanning utility, faces a burden of dealing with false positive. This aspect, therefore, demands imminent improvement for a more composed scanning result</span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">The scanner therefore presents various scans options like Full Scan, Custom Scan, or Critical Scan as shown in the image below.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"485\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto;\"></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">As a novice or expert user, you might ask yourself </span><em style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">“which devices and platforms are supported by Panda antivirus?</em><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> “. The answer is, panda security is compatible with a wide range of devices and OS. It supports most operating systems like Windows, Mac, and Android. For the case of windows OS, Panda antivirus solution still extends their services to old windows dated to Windows Vista and Windows XP on top of new windows (like windows 10) respectively. The services can also run on devices like laptops, phones, and Tablets </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">with an exception</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> for iPhones or iPads.&nbsp;</span></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">As far as ease of usability is concerned, Panda antivirus is a real gem. This is manifested on their appealing user interface that can allow any user whether a beginner or expert, to conveniently navigate through their application interfaces hassle-free. Most importantly, the essential features are well laid on the main screen, making users never bother looking for what they want.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">As a matter of fact, the latest update in its (Panda) product lines to the new Dome suites, present numerous improvements for users\' experience. These include a </span><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">quick and easy installation that can be completed with a single click, Data Shield function&nbsp;that enables users to specifically select files to be protected from ransomware, easy firewall configuration, etc.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">However, in the process of the installation, the user needs to pay attention if they don’t want to get the default setting on their search provider and home page.</span></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">In case you have issues (Technical or Non-Technical) or any inquiry to make regarding the service operation, Panda security got you covered, by offering a multitude of handy guides, tutorials, and general articles&nbsp;about several issues faced by their users. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">For scenarios that require more direct support, the clients can&nbsp;always reach the company via email, live chat, telephone, and even on social media (like twitter, or Panda-run community forum).</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto;\" width=\"521\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Note:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> Take to your consideration that most of the extended services are </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">only</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> provided by the premium plan.</span></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">The pricing plans and rates for Panda security are arrayed in different packages, namely: “</span><em style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Essential, Advanced, Complete and Premium”.</em><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> This wide range allows users to choose their plans based on valued features. For instance (i). The essential package only offers antivirus and firewalls with some privacy-protection tools, (ii). Advanced package, is more into privacy with features like parental controls, app locks, and a useful call blocker, (iii). The complete plan is a top-up to the remaining privacy features like data protection and password manager plus other mobile tools available. (iv). The premium package guarantees access to anonymous browsing with a VPN, cloud backup, and all technical support services on a 24/7 basis.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">All these plans come with a </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">30-day trial</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">, coupled with a </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">one-month money-back guarantee</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> in a circumstance whereby the client has decided to opt-out of the service. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">The subscription’s cost always fluctuates depending on the number of devices. Below is a breakdown of pricings per devices, however, the annual plan clients can save 25%.</span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><img src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" width=\"496\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto;\"></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-center\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\">Note:</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41); background-color: white;\"> the prices always increase with the number of devices and the subscriptions can be wired through Panda’s security Website using credit PayPal or Credit cards.</span></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">Of late, Panda security adopted some of the latest technology like Machine learning (ML) and artificial intelligence (AI), in a quest to conduct real-time threat hunting and to avert them (threats) right before affecting the targets system. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">For any internet user outside there, Panda antivirus is worth looking for, especially if your interest is towards </span><strong style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">protecting your devices and online privacy</strong><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">&nbsp;from anything (threats), at an affordable price. </span></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><span style=\"color: rgb(33, 37, 41);\">However to get the best from this product, it advisable to go for the relatively expensive premium package.</span></p>','2020-06-16 03:10:52','2020-06-19 08:43:21',NULL),(7,6,0,2,'<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaspersky is one of the finest, most tested, and awarded security software of the time, offering an easy-to-use interface, mighty real-time malware protection, with relatively zero impact on system performance. This product has been in the antivirus industry for over 20 years of operation, protecting approximately 400 + million users and employing over 3,500 employees across the globe.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaspersky security features are bundled in three major packages namely <strong>(i) Kaspersky antivirus</strong>, which is an essential product for windows platforms to block viruses and cryptocurrency mining malware <strong>(ii) Kaspersky Internet Security</strong>, an advanced security and antivirus suite for users privacy and money compatible with PC, Mac, and Mobile platforms <strong>(iii) Kaspersky total security</strong>, premium security &amp; antivirus suite for users and their kids, that can be run on PC, Mac &amp; mobile. Additionally, the products compose of formidable features like Security cloud, VPN secure connection, password manager, safe kids, rescue disk, and virus removal tools among others.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Note, the Kaspersky products are compatible with major platforms including, Windows, Mac, iOS, and Android among others. Also, the above security features come in both <strong>free-30 day’s trial</strong> and Paid version.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">According to numerous Lab tests, Kaspersky is presented with both Merits and Demerits. However, the good news is, the pros overshadows their down-size as displayed below.</p>','','[{\"value\":\"Low impact on system performance\"},{\"value\":\"Excellent set of features in top tier packages\"},{\"value\":\"TDSSKILLER feature on Free Kaspersky enables checking user’s computer for root kits and boot kits\"},{\"value\":\"Updated antivirus database\"},{\"value\":\"30-days free trial plan\"}]','[{\"value\":\"Does not guarantee  24/7 customer support\"},{\"value\":\"The entry-level package comes with a very limited set of features\"}]','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Amidst all the scandals and doubts on the credibility of the Kaspersky products, it remains the strongest security solution securing user’s devices against viruses and several tribes of malware.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Some of the notable security features by Kaspersky solution include but not limited to, <strong><em>malware protection,</em></strong> here it deploys a mechanism known as the Kaspersky Security Network (KSN) cloud and heuristic algorithms to protect users from the potential threats that haven’t yet been included in their malware database. That said, the malware protection is always in real-time with various scan options, cutting across detecting USB key-based malware, discovering and recovering damaged files, etc.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Other components that could be installed solitary to bolster the security dynamics are as follows, <strong><em>Kaspersky Cloud Protection</em></strong>, a feature optimized for protection against harmful applications and websites by enabling user’s computers to send data to the Kaspersky. <strong><em>Password Manager</em></strong> is a feature that can blend with password vault to store critical documents for the users like payment information. In brief, the password manager is used to secure online and offline credentials of the users through the creation of un-hackable passwords. <strong><em>Secure VPN</em>, <em>connection</em> </strong>this is very handy for internet users who frequently access the public or open WIFI connection. The feature helps to protect the client’s data from malicious users by providing&nbsp;a<strong> </strong>private connection to a secure network, not forgetting Kaspersky <strong><em>Safe money</em></strong> and <strong><em>privacy cleaner</em>.</strong></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">When it comes to this factor (Platforms Compatibility), Kaspersky made a tremendous effort to run in most of the well known Operating systems and devices. Typically, they can run on Windows, Mac, iOS, and Android respectively.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>However</strong>, subscriber planning for the entry-level package (<strong>Kaspersky Antivirus)</strong> would be limited to only the windows environment. But other top tiers packages are flexible and cover exclusively other platforms as indicated below.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"470\"></p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The operation and usage of the Kaspersky product do not require any “rocket science”. In other words, you don’t need to be a computer nerd to install, set and use these security solutions. Firstly, it has an intuitive user interface that supports simplistic navigation from one feature to another. Secondly, the installation process is straight-forward which runs at stunning speed compared to some of their rivals. Thirdly, Kaspersky inflicts very miniature impacts on the system performance. According to several AV lab tests, it turns out that it (Kaspersky) presents a range of 8-12 % when it comes to slowing down the system’s performance. This is so far one of the best and industry-leading percentages compared to other rivals, hitting an average percentage of 30%.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Via customer supports and services, Kaspersky solutions have vested a lot of efforts in presenting several avenues through which Techy and Non-Technical queries can be asked and resolved. Subscribers can freely access the Knowledge Base, FAQs to choose articles of their interest, Incase, they need direct contact with the support agent. It can be accomplished via chat, ticket system, or phone call supported in multiple languages. Furthermore, Kaspersky has active social media platforms and forums through which its subscribers can share the experience. Note that, this solution (Kaspersky) unfortunately<strong> does not support 24/7</strong> chat options, it only runs from 9 am-10 pm 7 days.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Kaspersky solution is one of the versatile products in the antivirus field with a multitude of features for the clients to choose, depending on their “wallets, security needs and numbers of the device”. One important thing to note though, this antivirus equally offers a <strong>30-days free trial version</strong> that could allow the new users to first test their services before considering a decision to join the Kaspersky family.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The paid versions are predominantly categorized under three major plans (Kaspersky Antivirus, Internet Security and Total security) with possession of varied features coupled with a money-back guarantee.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><br></p><p><img src=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\" width=\"407\"></p><p><br></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Note:</strong> The above image depicts the pricings and discounts at the time of writing this review. Besides, the initial cost for the first time subscribers is always far cheaper compared to the subsequent renewal plans. So, it is advisable to purchase this package 2 or 3 years half front to avoid incurring additional expenses.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Being one of the most tested and awarded security solutions across the globe, Kaspersky is indisputably a market leader in fighting the malware and virus infections by continuously updating their antivirus database engines.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Therefore, Kaspersky\'s solution got you covered whenever you intend to protect your PC, Mobile devices and the entire digital world.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Consequently, they fully fledge to protect against the latest virus, ransomware, spyware, and crypto lockers among other malicious programs and hacks.</p>','2020-06-16 04:00:55','2020-06-19 08:48:11',NULL),(8,2,0,1,'<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Norton is one of the Trouper in the Antivirus domain with impeccable features and performance when it comes to computers and internet security.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">The Norton products lines are jam-packed with <strong>(i) Comprehensive plans </strong>(Norton 360 Standard, Norton 360 Deluxe, and Norton 360 with LifeLock), <strong>(ii) Device Security</strong> (Norton Antivirus Plus and Norton security), <strong>(iii) Online Privacy </strong>(Norton secure VPN, Norton Privacy manager) and many more.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">In brief, this security solution offers, Antivirus, Anti-Spyware, Ransomware and Malware Protection, Online Threat Protection, Smart Firewall supports, Password Manager capability, Secure VPN, Dark Web Monitoring Powered by LifeLock, Bank &amp; Credit Card Activity Alerts, Court Records Scanning and parental control among others. Also, they can run on platforms like Windows, Mac, Linux, Android, and iOS respectively. Note, enthusiast users can download the trial version for testing before deciding to pay Norton services.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">There are numbers of Antivirus applications outside there, at the disposal of users. These vast quantum allow savvy users to decide on “what is good for them or not”. However, for the rookie users, it is a real-world bizarre (in terms of time taken, regrets, un-matching features, etc) while choosing antivirus of their choice. This is the reason why we want to simplify decision making for the users by laying the Merits and Demerits of Notion as follows.</p>','','[{\"value\":\"Compatible with Multiple platforms\"},{\"value\":\"A light-weight security solution\"},{\"value\":\"A strong defense against all types of malware.\"},{\"value\":\"Smart firewall with accurate abilities\"},{\"value\":\"Reliable file storage and backup options\"},{\"value\":\"Free 30 days trial version\"}]','[{\"value\":\"Constraints on 2-factor authentication for Password Manager\"},{\"value\":\"No Anti-Theft feature for iOS app.\"}]','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">Just like we discussed in the overview section, Norton products are absolutely loaded with handy security features. Here we took a quick look at some of the incomparable security &amp; privacy traits like <strong>Device security</strong>- in terms of excellent antivirus reputation scoring 100% protection rate on common and zero-day malware. <strong>Cloud backup</strong>- in various sizes, to provide secure remote storage for the user’s valuable documents and protection against ransomware<strong>. Secure VPN</strong>-with “no-log policy” to offer complete users anonymity. <strong>Password Manager</strong>- that creates a password vault to store the user’s credentials and generating a new complex password. Others are <strong>Parental Control</strong>, <strong>Safe Cam</strong>, etc.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><em>Note, parental control doesn\'t fully allow the parents to monitor the online communication of their children. Also, the VPN feature is a bit slow.</em></p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">That explained, Norton present several security packages in the market landscape, some of the major players include but not limited to:</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Norton Antivirus Plus</strong>- An entry-level product that provides flawless protection for user’s device and personal information in storage. The number of subscription stands at, one PC or Mac machine with 2GB cloud Backup. Additionally, there is online threat protection, smart firewall, Password manager, virus protection promise, not forgetting Anti-virus, Anti-spyware alongside protection against Malware and Ransomware&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Norton 360 Standard- </strong>This package provides its subscribers with a multi-layer of protection blended with online privacy in a single-tier solution compatible with<strong> </strong>iOS, and Android, besides the windows &amp; Mac OS. Similarly, the subscription is also one per a given machine. On top of the features in <strong>Antivirus Plus, </strong>it also has<strong> </strong>increased cloud storage up to 10GB, plus webcam protection alongside Dark Web monitoring features.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Norton 360 Deluxe</strong>&nbsp;This package is equal to the Standard package, except that, it can protect up 5 devices with 50GB of storage and parental control as added features.</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\"><strong>Norton 360 with LifeLock- </strong>is a holistic solution with additional features for protecting user’s devices, online privacy, and identities. Notably, the cloud storage is up to 100GB, with a million-dollar protection package and life lock identify alert system on top of all other traits in the above packs.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"ql-align-justify\">For more other additional security features, please don’t hesitate to check the official site of Norton that contains valuable information for the users.</p>','<p class=\"ql-align-justify\">This is one of the field where Norton performance is exceeding exceptional, In summary, Norton products runs on most Operating systems like Windows (from XP SP3 and abo